      "title": "Kite protest obstructed by Police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A Kite Festival to express dissent by the Aragalaya protestors was organized at Galle Face Green on Saturday, and Sri Lanka Police caused obstructions to this event.",
        "The protest was organized by a group of 'Aragalaya' activists.",
        "However, the relevant kite protest was later interrupted by the police."
      ],
